    {
      "id": "e269f4a2-478e-4f22-b5b5-78317f3135bf",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $(a_n)$ la suite réelle définie par :\n$a_0 = 1$, $2a_{n+1} = \\sum_{k=0}^n C_n^k a_ka_{n-k}$.\nOn pose $f(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty \\frac{a_n}{n!}x^n$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\((a_n)\\)</span> la suite réelle définie par : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_0 = 1\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2a_{n+1} = \\sum_{k=0}^n C_n^k a_ka_{n-k}\\)</span>. On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty \\frac{a_n}{n!}x^n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f0b2d612-46da-4769-8c23-f5721df34a2f",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que le rayon de convergence est non nul.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que le rayon de convergence est non nul.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "02283413-1596-4aea-95ca-f555e80b7663",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a_n \\le n!$ par récurrence.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_n \\le n!\\)</span> par récurrence.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8df01f81-7052-44f5-a461-f3728f53fd32",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $f(x)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
